ssible to the disabled. see theu.s. general services administrationpage.regardless of dollar amount, if your purchase of this product/service will affectmultiple end-users,csu policy requires you to follow theati procurement process.phone: 408-924-1558email:financeconnect@sjsu.edufinance and business servicessan jos state university60 south market streetsuite 470san jos, ca 95113